{"tid":485062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以陪我練倉頡","createTime":"2017-11-30T15:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T00:16:46.000Z","uid":53794,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e55af1ce0d4549bd100b3851b0de060b1a0bd1","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"利申返先我唔係小多士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過多幾個月就grad 要出嚟搵工<br />\n應該都係要做啲打字嘅工 依家學咗倉頡都三個月左右 一分鐘都唔知打唔打到30字 要加緊練習返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3807d57100c3fb68af4a7e197d59ec5129df71","tid":485062,"uid":160914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"打多啲就熟嘅啦！"},{"pid":"3836c52441035fda2fda881f03f5337edbf2f046","tid":485062,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"卜心竹水弓"},{"pid":"9c422dcd186f576b972caff6461d6fc6d088ac2f","tid":485062,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"卜心竹水弓"},{"pid":"a2d761e3f069e97556ae4657eba163d402dc47bc","tid":485062,"uid":155320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"加油 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好慶幸當年有打online game先學到打字"},{"pid":"86748fbab94addb32595c69bd8c4cb084a494085","tid":485062,"uid":120016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"以前都係靠啲電腦software練出黎"},{"pid":"ec1432001818e543b57be8ed8ced88ae92a3f5d5","tid":485062,"uid":160914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:30:58.000Z","msg":"卜弓月山金"},{"pid":"3416f46fb2ccbb9c72946f5f49af67892c242c96","tid":485062,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"咁你練啦<br />\n我三個字後返黎睇你練成點"},{"pid":"4efc668986e4790f4bd1ddc27fedb01324a9eccd","tid":485062,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"點幫你練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有人想幫我練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46dab227ca7954678553b6f3db2c54495ba73ee","tid":485062,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"what the hell are you talking about"},{"pid":"ffbe3b1d150a1d394b084dd39f5baa984a90b713","tid":485062,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"當年玩ICQ 練倉頡<br />\n而家啲人咁少係電腦面前，難練左"},{"pid":"65be1e36b13ee7f90af5f9574e422e56a86eb1c4","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點幫你練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有人想幫我練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係同我吹下水 乜都吹下 用多啲唔同嘅字<br />\n有時打一篇文有幾隻唔識打嘅字已經收皮<br />\n如果出到去in遇到啲咁嘅情況就麻煩"},{"pid":"eb4baa79abffd9a1ec036cd75de914d2410c8a04","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年玩ICQ 練倉頡<br />\n而家啲人咁少係電腦面前，難練左</blockquote><br />\n用手機打始終同電腦唔同 一定要返電腦練"},{"pid":"3273b58f4e41c2e309d07a7fd245a4c9db581609","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你練啦<br />\n我三個字後返黎睇你練成點</blockquote><br />\n好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893daf9a5ba9d14896fc3f5d89aa848c7b8391f5","tid":485062,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點幫你練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有人想幫我練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係同我吹下水 乜都吹下 用多啲唔同嘅字<br />\n有時打一篇文有幾隻唔識打嘅字已經收皮<br />\n如果出到去in遇到啲咁嘅情況就麻煩</blockquote><br />\n當年練倉頡玩倉頡過橋game"},{"pid":"3edcb5805623297f2c61d60b2bce050ec46162e5","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前都係靠啲電腦software練出黎</blockquote><br />\n個啲乜鳩野齊來學倉頡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8718bff7b2e43d6eada17b8f42f842cf6eaa0471","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卜心竹水弓</blockquote><br />\n無你咁好氣"},{"pid":"b2d12d528b4db8b64f29ebf26742413187e2a48f","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打多啲就熟嘅啦！</blockquote><br />\n所以係度搵人講下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efa60c300429f4b1d40046d18ab7d839514dd50","tid":485062,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>卜心竹水弓</blockquote><br />\n無你咁好氣</blockquote><br />\n無d恆心點得啊~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e1c5079b6848f568b6a9420e39da852e59d650","tid":485062,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>卜心竹水弓</blockquote><br />\n無你咁好氣</blockquote><br />\n無d恆心點得啊~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都話我唔係小多士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0766e35ed6ac9d850d460bfc905b2efd87e54b62","tid":485062,"uid":134964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"以前打九方，學極速成都學唔識，後來為咗搵工逼住學，索性直接學倉頡<br />\n<br />\n首先你要明白個原理，之後就揾啲文章喺電腦練，一開始畀自己睇住鍵盤上面啲倉頡碼，打得多就試下唔望鍵盤，打得多你見到啲字都可以唔使逐個碼拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67da38248ee923490e38e3273cb81746c50f50c6","tid":485062,"uid":2843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"記口訣就ok 啦<br />\n先上下，再左右，後外內<br />\n唔L 識就 頭碼+Z+尾碼<br />\n<br />\n想問多d tele me: lemonccc"},{"pid":"2e12fb954da80e7f74543b3ffabfb67ca4b6b186","tid":485062,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"討論區你想練到啲乜，起碼要即時通訊瘋狂吹水啦<br />\n當年同台仔鬥快打字互洗（有內容不過真係快到同講野無分別）<br />\n練就而家近百既成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e784276ac50c53d9ec833dd53b2cd664938c6d20","tid":485062,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前打九方，學極速成都學唔識，後來為咗搵工逼住學，索性直接學倉頡<br />\n<br />\n首先你要明白個原理，之後就揾啲文章喺電腦練，一開始畀自己睇住鍵盤上面啲倉頡碼，打得多就試下唔望鍵盤，打得多你見到啲字都可以唔使逐個碼拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倉頡最高境界係唔駛用腦去拆字，交俾隻手自己拆就掂"},{"pid":"022b49d3b2ab787782c58455c93d455aa1d1a1c0","tid":485062,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前打九方，學極速成都學唔識，後來為咗搵工逼住學，索性直接學倉頡<br />\n<br />\n首先你要明白個原理，之後就揾啲文章喺電腦練，一開始畀自己睇住鍵盤上面啲倉頡碼，打得多就試下唔望鍵盤，打得多你見到啲字都可以唔使逐個碼拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倉頡最高境界係唔駛用腦去拆字，交俾隻手自己拆就掂</blockquote><br />\n我打左廿年<br />\n我而家都係咁"}]}